# Emborg

> Front-end to Borg Backup
> More information: <https://emborg.readthedocs.io/en/stable/index.html>

- Choose a configuration (global to emborg)

`emborg -c <configuration>`

- Do a backup for default configuration

`emborg create`

- List existing backup 

`emborg list`

- Do a backup for a configuration with list and stats

`emborg -c <config> create -l -s`
